that we are very, um,

00:00:48.482 --> 00:00:52.881
supportive of the civilians right to self determination to civilians,

00:00:52.882 --> 00:00:54.281
right to dignity,

00:00:54.282 --> 00:00:57.501
to humans, right to life.

00:00:57.960 --> 00:01:04.140
