00:01:16.000 --> 00:01:17.600
because I think it's important.

00:01:17.601 --> 00:01:20.761
There are a lot of people talking about how to combat

00:01:20.762 --> 00:01:21.921
anti Semitism on this app,

00:01:21.922 --> 00:01:25.641
but a lot of them are doing it from a pro Israel standpoint

00:01:25.642 --> 00:01:26.641
in my opinion.

00:01:26.642 --> 00:01:27.001
Unfortunately,

00:01:27.002 --> 00:01:29.181
I think that just causes more

00:01:29.840 --> 00:01:35.440
black and white team type mentalities with both of these issues.

00:01:35.441 --> 00:01:39.441
Because you can believe in the dignity of all humans.

00:01:39.442 --> 00:01:41.241
And there's a lot of people on both sides

00:01:41.242 --> 00:01:43.721
that are ignoring the humanity of each other.

00:01:43.722 --> 00:01:45.421
I wanna help people.

00:01:45.520 --> 00:01:47.580
I want to help civilians.

00:01:47.920 --> 00:01:49.440
